  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/e402a18df8a69de116177b315d462ee9.avif?t=1756921714\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras_big/e402a18df8a69de116177b315d462ee9.avif?t=1756921714 width=800 height=286 /></span><strong>Fart King – The Ultimate Precision Platforming Challenge!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A determined pug, a legendary crown, and only one way to reach it—by mastering the power of fart propulsion! <i>Fart King</i> is a hardcore platformer where every jump is a test of skill, and every mistake sends you plummeting back down. Can you control your toots well enough to reach the top?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/e96f742c4b7c8ee9ce4f17150d214b02.poster.avif?t=1756921714\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/e96f742c4b7c8ee9ce4f17150d214b02.webm?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/e96f742c4b7c8ee9ce4f17150d214b02.mp4?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💨 <strong>High-Stakes Jumping!</strong><br> The only way forward is up, and gravity is your greatest enemy. One wrong move, and you'll face a long, painful fall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐶 <strong>Master the Art of the Fart!</strong><br> Every jump demands precision, patience, and nerves of steel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/48c550117041e48e3d4b4865f71d604e.poster.avif?t=1756921714\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/48c550117041e48e3d4b4865f71d604e.webm?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/48c550117041e48e3d4b4865f71d604e.mp4?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 <strong>Plan Every Jump!</strong><br> Not every path is the right one. Think before you leap, because once you're airborne, there's no turning back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>A Test of True Endurance!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A deceptively simple but incredibly challenging experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with friends to see who can claim the Fart Crown first!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Addictive gameplay that rewards skill and persistence. <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/99875c741910c8c0539f8faafb39982b.poster.avif?t=1756921714\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/99875c741910c8c0539f8faafb39982b.webm?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/99875c741910c8c0539f8faafb39982b.mp4?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Struggling? The Dev is Watching...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/ca495b4ece60b5650e1465223f0d8760.poster.avif?t=1756921714\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/ca495b4ece60b5650e1465223f0d8760.webm?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/ca495b4ece60b5650e1465223f0d8760.mp4?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😅 Fall too often, and the developer himself might show up to roast your skills. But don’t worry—he’s not all mean. He might just bless you with a little help: wings, a rocket, or even a teleport... if you’ve truly earned his pity. Being a noob has its perks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠 <strong>Practice Mode!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/f7a97e8dcfa14f69e6706c74264ba594.poster.avif?t=1756921714\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/f7a97e8dcfa14f69e6706c74264ba594.webm?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/f7a97e8dcfa14f69e6706c74264ba594.mp4?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place checkpoints and respawn instantly to practice tough jumps.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Atmosphere:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/02c6adb1dd76858c4cb9b238ecea01aa.poster.avif?t=1756921714\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/02c6adb1dd76858c4cb9b238ecea01aa.webm?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/02c6adb1dd76858c4cb9b238ecea01aa.mp4?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🎨 Charming pixel-art visuals with smooth animations.<br> 🔊 <strong>Choose your fart sounds!</strong> Turn on realistic, juicy fart effects for full immersion, or switch to cute 8-bit sounds if you’d rather not hear toots for hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ve come this far—will you rise to glory, or will your journey end in a humiliating fall? Only the most skilled players can become the <strong>Fart King!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/e402a18df8a69de116177b315d462ee9.avif?t=1756921714\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras_big/e402a18df8a69de116177b315d462ee9.avif?t=1756921714 width=800 height=286 /></span><strong>Fart King – The Ultimate Precision Platforming Challenge!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A determined pug, a legendary crown, and only one way to reach it—by mastering the power of fart propulsion! <i>Fart King</i> is a hardcore platformer where every jump is a test of skill, and every mistake sends you plummeting back down. Can you control your toots well enough to reach the top?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/e96f742c4b7c8ee9ce4f17150d214b02.poster.avif?t=1756921714\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/e96f742c4b7c8ee9ce4f17150d214b02.webm?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3630870/extras/e96f742c4b7c8ee9ce4f17150d214b02.mp4?t=1756921714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💨 <strong>High-Stakes Jumping!</strong><br> The only way forward is up, and gravity is your greatest enemy. One wrong move, and you'll face a long, painful fall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐶 <strong>Master the Art of the Fart!</strong><br> Every jump demands precision, patience, and nerves of steel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.s